白ﾙ@e7ff35f38d64f2f451cc7962f749d59e2bcde98b96811a1e008a0e42baeab7bbﾚｬTitle: This week in Nushell #234
Path: Nushell
Content:
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11859] simplified input types for 
``select``
 and 
``reject``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11858] removed the required positional arg for some file system commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11809] fixed an error message for 
``headers``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11808] prevented duplicate keys for 
``lazy make``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11807] prevented duplicate record keys when decoding from nuon
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11803] added the ability to cast a dataframe's column to a different datatype
kit494way 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11864] fixed 
``commandline --cursor``
 to return an int
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11861] fixed an issue building for riscv64
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11857] disallowed spreading lists automatically when calling externals
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11856] updated default_config with new defaults
, and bumped the reedline version (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11844] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11840] 2
)
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11855] fixed 
``workspace.members``
 for dependabot
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11852] moved 
``du``
 from platform to filesystem
nibon7 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11848] bumped polars from 0.36 to 0.37
dannou812 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11846] fixed date formatting in 
``to/from toml``
0323pin 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11823] fixed a build failure on NetBSD
CAD97 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11822] simplified prompt tilde substitution
